column2: Sunny- 6-10" waves- start of algae blooms
Sunny- slight waves- evenings killed algae bloom- dark green floating slicks on windward side of lake
Partly cloudy- windy- 8-12" waves- water temp dropping
Stained water- partly cloudy- very windy.  Waves at times 12-16".
Partly cloudy- calm water- water temp is 38 degrees- 3/4 of the lake was ice covered this morning.  Last reading of the year.
Stained water- ice went out April 16- waves slight.
Stained water- sunny- waves slight.  Clearest water I have ever seen.
Stained water.  Heavy rains all week.
Public perception due to stained water.
Stained water- some suspended and floating algae present in parts of lake.
Very high water- floating and suspended algae- possible lake turnover.
Water green from algae- brown from stain.  Floating and suspended algae- thick layer on down wind side of lake.
Still suspended and floating algae- weeds starting to die off in certain spots
Stained water- very windy last 4 days- surface water temp. 50 degrees- sunny today- water clearing.
Stained water- mild wind from south- overcast- water temp. 48 degrees surface- last reading.
Stained water.  Very windy last 2 days- sunny today.
Hot and humid- sunny with mild breeze.
Also stained water.  Lake about 1' foot down.
Also stained water.  Lake about 1' down- very windy last 2 days.
Very windy- first green surface film.
Stained water.  Surface film/heavy rain day before.
Stained water.  Turn-over complete- very windy.
Stained water- 47 degrees water temp. top to bottom.
Stained water- very windy- shore ice up to 60' out in places.  Last reading for 1995.
Stained water. first reading 1996. ice went out 13-15 days ago. water has lots of suspended matter. looks like it does after fall turn over.
Windy/rain.  Temperature at 3-6-9- and 12 feet is 65 degrees.
Stained water. 74 degrees surface temp. heavy rain last night.
Sunny- moderate wind and waves.  I believe we had a minor algae bloom mostly around the shore.
Stained water.  Sunny- mild wind and waves- also algae blooms but not heavy.
Stained water.  Water very high- lots of suspended matter in water.
Little wind- very calm surface- water is slightly green from algae but not too bad.
Stained water. very windy 1 to 1 1/2 foot. waves-preturnover.
Partly cloudy- SE moderate wind- 1' waves.
Stained water. northwest wind- skim ice out to 150' from shore in spots.
Stained water. northwest wind- snowing skim ice up to 100' from shore.
Stained water.  Sunny- water calm.  Surface temperature 74 degrees.
Calm.  No wind.  Rain all day 2 days ago. a lot of suspended algae.
Stained water.  Overcast.  Southeast wind.  Rained yesterday.
Start of turn over.  Suspended matter in water.
